Scijava-based GUIs for SNT built-in commands.

    ChooseDatasetCmd
    Implements the 'Choose Tracing Image (From Open Image)...' command.
    ColorMapReconstructionCmd
    Implements Reconstruction Viewer's 'Color coding' commands.

    Command class for GUI commands extending DynamicCommand

Package sc.fiji.snt.gui.cmds Description

Scijava-based GUIs for SNT built-in commands. There should not be a need to script these directly. However, the source code of these simple Commands exemplifies how to script SNTService
Author:
Tiago Ferreira
